h6.span: Do You ever mistakenly put a wrong Customer in Sales Order and wonder how you can fix it?
Or do You wish to change your SO's Customer as you need without cancelling all it's related documents?
Well, You Found The Right Module!

span.font: Allows you to change your Customer in validated Sales Order
After revised Customer is set, it will update it's all related documents just by clicking a button.
Picking Orders, Invoice, Journal Entries & Items data
You can set this privilege for certain user only

div.ol:
This module need dependencies (other modules) to run. It's called ​​"Base of Rename Module", You can download it for free.
Download this module and also "Base of Rename Module", then put it inside your Odoo Addons folder.
From Your Odoo interface, enter the settings menu > Activate the Developer Mode
Then, from your main menu go into Apps > Update Apps List > Update.
Install "Base of Rename Module" first, and then install this module.
Go to the Settings Menu > User & Companies > Select User.
Grant privileges to that User by changing the Rename Privilege selection
Refresh the user's browser, they will be able to change purchase order's vendor
Note : If you also installing another "Replace Module", you will see the selection mode become the checkbox button. It's not a problem and will not going to affect anything.
